<div class="page-header">
    <h1 id="beekeeping_top">Beekeeping Controller Hierarchy</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Reference for <code>Controller::Beekeeping</code> and its sub-controllers — the canonical home for all beekeeping feature routes.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-container">
<div class="content-primary">

<nav class="app-section">
    <ul class="inline-nav">
        <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#beekeeping-pm">Beekeeping.pm</a></li>
