<div class="app-section">
    <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
    <div class="content-section">
        <p>The <strong>Beekeeping controller hierarchy</strong> was introduced in May 2026 to resolve an architectural ambiguity. Previously, all beekeeping feature routes lived under <code>/BMaster/*</code> inside <code>Controller::BMaster</code> — the same controller that serves the BMaster <em>site home</em>. This made it impossible to distinguish between "BMaster as a Comserv SiteName" and "BMaster as a beekeeping application feature."</p>

        <p>The refactoring separates these concerns cleanly:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>Controller::BMaster</code> — owns <code>/BMaster</code> (the site home only). All old feature routes redirect to <code>/Beekeeping/*</code>.</li>
            <li><code>Controller::Beekeeping</code> (and sub-controllers) — owns all beekeeping feature routes under <code>/Beekeeping/*</code>.</li>
            <li><code>Controller::Apiary</code> — owns the member-only apiary management tools under <code>/Apiary/*</code> (unchanged).</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Audience split</h3>
        <table class="data-table">
            <thead>
                <tr><th>Audience</th><th>Controller</th><th>URL prefix</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr><td>Guests / public</td><td><code>Beekeeping</code></td><td><code>/Beekeeping/*</code></td><td>Education, information, membership pitch</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Members (logged in)</td><td><code>Apiary</code></td><td><code>/Apiary/*</code></td><td>Hive tracking, inspections, queen rearing, health</td></tr>
                <tr><td>BMaster site entry</td><td><code>BMaster</code></td><td><code>/BMaster</code></td><td>Site landing page only</td></tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="app-section">
    <h2 id="beekeeping-pm"><code>Controller::Beekeeping</code> (<code>Beekeeping.pm</code>)</h2>
    <div class="content-section">
        <p><strong>File:</strong> <code>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Controller/Beekeeping.pm</code></p>
        <p><strong>Base chain:</strong> <code>:Chained('/') :PathPart('Beekeeping') :CaptureArgs(0)</code></p>

        <table class="data-table">
            <thead>
                <tr><th>Action</th><th>Attr</th><th>URL</th><th>Template / destination</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>base</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Chained('/') :PathPart('Beekeeping') :CaptureArgs(0)</code></td>
                    <td>—</td>
                    <td>Chain root — no output</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>index</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Chained('base') :PathPart('') :Args(0)</code></td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping"><code>/Beekeeping</code></a></td>
                    <td><code>BMaster/BMaster.tt</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>bee_pasture</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Path('/Beekeeping/bee_pasture') :Args(0)</code></td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/bee_pasture"><code>/Beekeeping/bee_pasture</code></a></td>
                    <td>Redirect → <code>/ENCY/BeePastureView</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>apiary</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Path('/Beekeeping/apiary') :Args(0)</code></td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/apiary"><code>/Beekeeping/apiary</code></a></td>
                    <td>Guests: <code>Beekeeping/apiary.tt</code> — Members: redirect → <code>/Apiary</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>queens</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Path('/Beekeeping/Queens') :Args(0)</code></td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/Queens"><code>/Beekeeping/Queens</code></a></td>
                    <td>Redirect → <code>/Apiary/QueenRearing</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>hive</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Path('/Beekeeping/hive') :Args(0)</code></td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/hive"><code>/Beekeeping/hive</code></a></td>
                    <td>Redirect → <code>/Apiary/HiveManagement</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>environment</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Path('/Beekeeping/environment') :Args(0)</code></td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/environment"><code>/Beekeeping/environment</code></a></td>
                    <td><code>Beekeeping/environment.tt</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>education</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Path('/Beekeeping/education') :Args(0)</code></td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/education"><code>/Beekeeping/education</code></a></td>
                    <td><code>Beekeeping/education.tt</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>products</code></td>
                    <td><code>:Path('/Beekeeping/products') :Args(0)</code></td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/products"><code>/Beekeeping/products</code></a></td>
                    <td><code>Beekeeping/products.tt</code></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="app-section">
    <h2 id="yards-pm"><code>Controller::Beekeeping::Yards</code> (<code>Beekeeping/Yards.pm</code>)</h2>
    <div class="content-section">
        <p><strong>File:</strong> <code>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Controller/Beekeeping/Yards.pm</code></p>
        <p>Manages yard listing and creation. Uses <code>$c->model('DBEncy')->resultset('Beekeeping::Yard')</code> directly for simplicity.</p>

        <table class="data-table">
            <thead>
                <tr><th>Action</th><th>Method</th><th>URL</th><th>Template</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>yards</code></td>
                    <td>GET</td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/yards"><code>/Beekeeping/yards</code></a></td>
                    <td><code>Beekeeping/Yards/index.tt</code></td>
                    <td>Lists all yards for <code>session.SiteName</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>add_yard</code></td>
                    <td>GET + POST</td>
                    <td><a href="/Beekeeping/add_yard"><code>/Beekeeping/add_yard</code></a></td>
                    <td><code>Beekeeping/Yards/add.tt</code></td>
                    <td>GET renders form; POST creates yard, redirects to <code>/Beekeeping/yards</code></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3>Yard form fields (POST)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><code>yard_code</code> — unique identifier (required)</li>
            <li><code>yard_name</code> — display name (required)</li>
            <li><code>sitename</code> — pre-filled from session, readonly in form</li>
            <li><code>total_yard_size</code> — max hive count (required)</li>
            <li><code>date_established</code> — date (required)</li>
            <li><code>notes</code> — freetext</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="app-section">
    <h2 id="health-pm"><code>Controller::Beekeeping::Health</code> (<code>Beekeeping/Health.pm</code>)</h2>
